											</p>

											<div class="small d-flex justify-content-end mt-5 mb-2 me-2">
												<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary me-2 ">Reply</button>
												<form method="post" action="/pays/5" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to delete this item?');">
													<input type="hidden" name="_token" value="fbf9a52e681a8e5e.75SUCoJt_HjhcOEkHBx5SV74WFKrLXBTasWYmS3841w.ws6jONZYvw-pJq5AUmoMeivNLj3TeRhlXYPb2H_OqD2uzMxh-ySpINRdkg">
